author: Nintendo of America
description:
Face your nightmares in EL COCO, out now on Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/el-coco-switch/?utm_source=SW&utm_medium=soytnoa&utm_campaign=P1021-01&utm_id=P1021-01    

Play as Ky, a small, lost soul trapped in an unknown dream realm filled with broken memories and living nightmares. To escape, you must descend deeper into The Uncertain and face unknown horrors to recover what was lost. But be careful—the further the descent, the more dangerous the journey becomes.
